大海的力量，就知擋不住的。<br />\n<br />\n李小加接受《香港經濟日報》訪問時，分析中美大國關係之間，「上層是意識形態，中層是物理經濟、政府固體一樣的東西，金融是Liquid（液體）。液體不可能像固體一樣，輕易一個政策一來，一搬就搬過去。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:21:47.000Z","msg":"唔怕你精，唔怕你呆，最怕你唔來<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cee07e8ff24566fc1c1b95c447f503d50b0c5eb3","tid":2345112,"uid":292544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"又講到咁明姓支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a95c3688ba2c4883787a91c11a72775a19db77c","tid":2345112,"uid":71071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:23:57.000Z","msg":"屌，蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7023425a70c9e1ea00f917570c564f2be3021180","tid":2345112,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:24:25.000Z","msg":"睇完小蟻套鬧劇仲撚有人信支那有金融市場？<br />\n<br />\n全部都係老千局<br />\n<br />\n仲買港股正on9"},{"pid":"ca75cc0b85f3fea625fdaaee99b0bb53e5cf3e24","tid":2345112,"uid":34557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"排位：1. 不姓美 2. 不姓中<br />\n意思係咪 就算姓都係姓美先！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18bf964de2e1bfe36b1c167c84ba22715a7d8274","tid":2345112,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"再嘈 美國連港交所都制裁埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e3c468edeec309f8dfa180f27be7b35f86d10e","tid":2345112,"uid":63336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T10:39:45.000Z","msg":"咁多嘢講，捉佢同馬雲一齊通櫃"},{"pid":"851bcda778818467ad62cd2a908635828f88cb9d","tid":234511